#: ReviewsController.php:358
#. translators: %1$s: Plugin name, %2$s: Time period (e.g., "1 week", "1 month")
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hey, you've been using %1$s for %2$s on your site. We hope the plugin has "
"been useful. Please could you quickly leave a 5-star rating on "
"WordPress.org? It really does help to keep %1$s growing."
msgstr ""
"Hai, Anda telah menggunakan %1$s selama %2$s di situs Anda. Kami berharap "
"plugin ini bermanfaat. Tolong, bisakah Anda dengan cepat meninggalkan "
"penilaian 5 bintang di WordPress.org? Itu benar-benar membantu untuk "
"menjaga %1$s agar terus berkembang."

#: ReviewsController.php:369
msgid "1 week"
msgstr "1 minggu"

#: ReviewsController.php:377
msgid "1 month"
msgstr "1 bulan"

#: ReviewsController.php:388
msgid "3 months"
msgstr "3 bulan"

#: ReviewsController.php:643
#. translators: %s: Plugin name
#, php-format
msgid "Click here to add your rating for %s"
msgstr "Klik di sini untuk menambahkan penilaian Anda untuk %s"

#: ReviewsController.php:649
msgid "Maybe later"
msgstr "Mungkin nanti"

#: ReviewsController.php:654
msgid "I already did"
msgstr "Saya sudah melakukannya"
